title: Kelsey Cook
itunes:title: Kelsey Cook
description:
Dewers! My #HoneyDew this week comes from Hall of Fame foosball roots and she seriously wouldn't be alive today if it weren't for table soccer! Kelsey Cook joins me on The Dew to talk about her parents’ divorce and her incredibly honest and open relationship with her mom - like so open she asked her mom to go to a movie so she and her boyfriend could lose their virginities - and her mom did! We talk about an ex-boyfriend with borderline personality disorder and the dangers that come with living in a one bathroom home when you have irritable bowel syndrome. Subscribe, rate & review!
